text.section:
Any person who applies to be a commercial motor vehicle driver shall provide the employer, at the time of the application, with the following information for the ten (10) years preceding the date of application whenever the information is available:
A list of the names and addresses of the applicant's previous employers for which the applicant was a driver of a commercial motor vehicle;
The dates during which the applicant drove for each employer;
The reason for leaving that employer; and
A certification that all information furnished is true and complete.
